OL,3,C'Dangerous' man who stabbed father on
OL,4,Cdoorstep of flat found guilty of murder
OL,6,FA 39-year-old has been found guilty of
OL,7,Fmurdering a 'loving' father inside a
OL,8,Fblock of flats in Gloucester city
OL,9,Fcentre.
OL,11,FPolice bodyworn camera footage shows
OL,12,Fthe moment officers arrested Kane
OL,13,FKotwica in Gloucester after he had
OL,14,Ffatally stabbed Matthew Cainey to
OL,15,Fdeath hours earlier on Bedford Street.
OL,17,FHe claimed he stabbed to the 53-year-
OL,18,Fold to death in self-defence at the
OL,19,Fflat after an argument on 28 May, but
OL,20,Fa jury at Bristol Crown Court did not
OL,21,Fbelieve him.
