OL,3,C'Dangerous' man who stabbed father on
OL,4,Cdoorstep of flat found guilty of murder
OL,6,FDuring a three-week trial, jurors
OL,7,Fheard that Kotwica had been in the
OL,8,Fflat with Mr Cainey, two other men and
OL,9,Ftwo women.
OL,11,FThe court heard Kotwica grabbed a
OL,12,Fknife from the kitchen during an
OL,13,Fargument with one of the men, and
OL,14,Fbegan threatening him with it. But the
OL,15,Fweapon was taken from him by one of
OL,16,Fthe women and the soon-to-be-killer
OL,17,Fleft the flat.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
