OL,3,C'Dangerous' man who stabbed father on
OL,4,Cdoorstep of flat found guilty of murder
OL,6,FJurors were told Kutwica patrolled
OL,7,Faround the area for nearly an hour and
OL,8,Fa half before returning to the flat
OL,9,Farmed with a knife that was hidden in
OL,10,Fthe pocket of his hoody.
OL,12,FWhen Mr Cainey answered the door,
OL,13,FKutwica fatally stabbed him as he
OL,14,Fstood in the hallway of the flat.
OL,16,FDuring the attack, another men was
OL,17,Falso stabbed in the chest and had to
OL,18,Fundergo life-saving surgery while a
OL,19,Fthird man suffered a significant and
OL,20,Fvery serious wound to his neck, the
OL,21,Fcourt was told.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
