OL,3,C'Dangerous' man who stabbed father on
OL,4,Cdoorstep of flat found guilty of murder
OL,6,FAfter running away from the flat, CCTV
OL,7,Fcaptured Kotwica throwing the knife
OL,8,Fdown a drain. It was later recovered
OL,9,Fby officers.
OL,11,FHe was arrested nearby by armed
OL,12,Fofficers and following an
OL,13,Finvestigation, he was charged with
OL,14,Fmurder and two attempted murders and
OL,15,Fremanded into custody.
OL,17,FFollowing a trial, Kotwica was found
OL,18,Fnot guilty of the attempted murders of
OL,19,Fthe two men, but found guilty of two
OL,20,Fcounts of grievous bodily harm with
OL,21,Fintent.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
