OL,3,C'Dangerous' man who stabbed father on
OL,4,Cdoorstep of flat found guilty of murder
OL,6,FHe was remanded in custody and is due
OL,7,Fto be sentenced at Bristol Crown Court
OL,8,Fon 10 December.
OL,10,F'Dangerous and violent man'
OL,12,FDetective Inspector Adam Stacey of the
OL,13,FGloucestershire Police Major Crime
OL,14,FInvestigation Team, who led the
OL,15,Finvestigation, said: "Kane Kotwica is
OL,16,Fa very dangerous and violent
OL,17,Findividual whose pre-meditated
OL,18,Fcowardly attack has robbed a family of
OL,19,Ftheir loved one and caused serious
OL,20,Finjury to two others.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
