OL,3,C'Dangerous' man who stabbed father on
OL,4,Cdoorstep of flat found guilty of murder
OL,6,F"My thoughts remain with the family
OL,7,Fand loved ones of Matthew, who have
OL,8,Fshown incredible dignity throughout
OL,9,Fall of this, not least in court when
OL,10,Flistening to Kotwica's evidence.
OL,12,F"It has been an incredibly traumatic
OL,13,Fand upsetting time for them so I hope
OL,14,Fthat today's verdict brings them some
OL,15,Fcomfort."
OL,17,F'He was always there for people':
OL,18,FFamily remembers Matthew Cainey
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
